Open this file in Android studio or tak the .akp file in any android phone to get started. Now in Android studio, when the files are build succesfully, click on Run button. An android emulator will run this app. As this app will launch, user will able to see a logo and title on a screen and then it will proceed to a login page. Here, if the user dont have an account with this app, click on create new account link. And register. Then user will able to login. User will be directed to Home activity. On the top left there is a drawer button where user can switch to differnt activites lice post, profile and logout. 
